org.hibernate.testing.logger

Class Log4DelegatingLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jboss.logging.Logger
      • org.hibernate.testing.logger.Log4DelegatingLogger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, org.jboss.logging.BasicLogger

    public final class Log4DelegatingLogger
extends org.jboss.logging.Logger
    A Logger implementation which delegates to Log4J but makes it possible to test for events being logged (not logged).
